a local café, soaking in Victoria’s small-town charm.'),(242,49,3,'Sunset Cruise & Farewell','Embark on a sunset cruise from Beau Vallon, sailing along Mahé’s coast with champagne in hand. Watch the sky blaze with color as you spot silhouettes of distant islands. Savor a farewell dinner of Creole fish curry, celebrating Beau Vallon’s coastal allure.'),(243,50,1,'Beau Vallon & Snorkeling','Relax on Beau Vallon Beach, snorkeling among coral reefs teeming with angelfish and sea turtles. Try stand-up paddleboarding along the calm shoreline, guided by local experts. Savor a lunch of grilled prawns at a beachside shack, with waves lapping at your feet.'),(244,50,2,'Victoria Botanical Gardens','Explore Victoria’s Botanical Gardens, strolling through palm groves and meeting giant tortoises. Visit the orchid house, marveling at vibrant blooms unique to the Seychelles. Savor a fruit salad lunch at the garden café, surrounded by tropical greenery.'),(245,50,3,'Anse Intendance & Takamaka','Lounge on Anse Intendance, a wild beach with powdery sand and dramatic waves, perfect for surfing. Tour the Takamaka Rum Distillery, sampling spiced rum and learning about Creole distillation. Savor a Creole barbecue dinner, enjoying the beach’s untamed beauty.'),(246,50,4,'Morne Seychellois Trek','Hike Morne Seychellois National Park, ascending to misty peaks with views of Mahé’s coastline and distant atolls. Spot endemic birds like the Seychelles bulbul amidst lush rainforests. Enjoy a picnic lunch by a hidden stream, immersed in the park’s tranquility.'),(247,50,5,'Creole Cooking Class','Join a Creole cooking class in Victoria, learning to prepare dishes like fish curry and ladob with fresh coconut milk. Shop for ingredients at a local market, discovering Seychellois herbs and spices. Savor your creations at a communal lunch, sharing stories with fellow travelers.'),(248,50,6,'Port Launay & Farewell','Snorkel at Port Launay Marine Park, swimming among vibrant corals and schools of tropical