e Abyssinian Baptist. Visit the Apollo Theater, learning about its legacy in jazz and soul music. Savor a soul food lunch of fried chicken and collard greens, celebrating Harlem’s cultural richness.'),(269,54,7,'Broadway & Times Square','Experience a Broadway show, captivated by world-class performances in the Theater District. Wander Times Square at night, dazzled by LED screens and street musicians. Savor a farewell dinner of New York-style pizza, toasting to the city’s endless energy.'),(270,55,1,'The Strip & Bellagio Fountains','Stroll the Las Vegas Strip, marveling at themed resorts like the Venetian and Caesars Palace. Watch the Bellagio Fountains’ choreographed water show, set to music under dazzling lights. Savor a steak dinner at a Strip restaurant, soaking in Vegas’s glitzy ambiance.'),(271,55,2,'Fremont Street Experience','Explore Fremont Street, zipping down the SlotZilla zipline under a vibrant digital canopy. Enjoy live music and street performers, trying your luck at historic casinos like the Golden Nugget. Savor a shrimp cocktail at a retro diner, embracing old Vegas charm.'),(272,55,3,'High Roller & LINQ Promenade','Ride the High Roller, the world’s tallest observation wheel, for panoramic views of the Strip and desert. Wander the LINQ Promenade, shopping and sampling desserts at Sprinkles Cupcake ATM. Savor a farewell buffet dinner, celebrating Vegas’s over-the-top energy.'),(273,56,1,'The Strip & Vegas Icons','Tour the Las Vegas Strip, exploring the Luxor’s pyramid and New York-New York’s skyline replica. Watch the Bellagio Fountains dance to classic tunes, a Vegas must-see. Savor a dinner of lobster tail at a celebrity chef restaurant, immersed in the Strip’s glamour.'),(274,56,2,'Grand Canyon South Rim','Journey to the Grand Canyon’s South Rim, hiking along the Rim Trail for breathtaking views of the vast chasm. Learn about the canyon’s geology at the Yavapai Point Museum, spotting condors soaring overhead. Savor a picnic lunch at Mather Point, 