rt. Join a guided tour to uncover stories behind the museum’s vast collections. Savor a farewell lunch of butter tarts, celebrating Toronto’s cultural richness.'),(282,58,1,'CN Tower & Ripley’s Aquarium','Visit the CN Tower, daring to walk the EdgeWalk or relaxing at the 360 Restaurant with city views. Explore Ripley’s Aquarium, marveling at jellyfish and sharks in underwater tunnels. Savor a dinner of Lake Ontario perch, soaking in Toronto’s waterfront energy.'),(283,58,2,'Niagara Falls Day Trip','Journey to Niagara Falls, cruising on the Hornblower to feel the mist of the thundering cascades. Stroll Clifton Hill, enjoying quirky attractions and panoramic views from the Skylon Tower. Savor a lunch of Niagara wine and charcuterie, with the falls roaring nearby.'),(284,58,3,'Distillery & Kensington Market','Tour the Distillery District, sampling spirits at a local brewery and browsing unique boutiques. Wander Kensington Market’s eclectic streets, tasting global street food like empanadas and bao buns. Savor a dinner of farm-to-table cuisine, celebrating Toronto’s diversity.'),(285,58,4,'Algonquin Park Adventure','Explore Algonquin Provincial Park, canoeing on serene lakes and spotting moose along forested trails. Join a guided wolf howl, listening for replies under the starry sky. Savor a campfire dinner of bannock and chili, immersed in Ontario’s wilderness.'),(286,58,5,'Casa Loma & Yorkville','Tour Casa Loma, a Gothic Revival castle with secret passages and sprawling gardens. Stroll Yorkville’s chic streets, browsing designer boutiques and art galleries. Savor a dinner of maple-glazed duck, reflecting on Toronto’s blend of history and luxury.'),(287,58,6,'Royal Ontario Museum & Bloor','Visit the ROM, exploring its vast galleries of ancient artifacts and natural history exhibits. Wander Bloor Street, shopping at high-end stores and sipping coffee at a trendy café. Savor a dinner of Ontario lamb, celebrating the city’s cultural depth.'),(288,58,7,'Harbourfront & Fare