nd cultural treasures.'),(308,62,6,'Roma & Condesa','Wander the trendy Roma and Condesa neighborhoods, admiring Art Deco architecture and vibrant street art. Visit local cafés, sampling churros and Mexican hot chocolate. Savor a dinner of cochinita pibil, celebrating Mexico City’s modern culinary scene.'),(309,62,7,'Bellas Artes & Farewell','Tour Palacio de Bellas Artes, marveling at its Tiffany glass curtain and Siqueiros murals. Stroll the historic center, shopping for silver jewelry and Talavera pottery. Savor a farewell dinner of pozole, toasting to Mexico City’s vibrant heritage.'),(310,63,1,'Playa Delfines & Hotel Zone','Relax on Playa Delfines, Cancun’s most scenic beach, swimming in turquoise waters and snapping photos at the colorful Cancun sign. Explore the Hotel Zone, browsing beachfront boutiques and sipping margaritas. Savor a lunch of ceviche, with the Caribbean breeze cooling the sunny afternoon.'),(311,63,2,'Chichen Itza Day Trip','Visit Chichen Itza, marveling at the Kukulkan Pyramid and the ancient ballcourt with a guided tour. Explore the sacred Cenote Ik Kil, swimming in its crystal-clear waters surrounded by vines. Savor a lunch of pollo pibil, reflecting on the Maya’s architectural genius.'),(312,63,3,'Tulum Ruins & Beach','Tour Tulum’s cliffside Mayan ruins, overlooking the turquoise Caribbean Sea and iguana-filled grounds. Relax on Tulum’s white-sand beach, snorkeling or lounging under palapas. Savor a dinner of grilled fish tacos, enjoying Tulum’s bohemian coastal vibe.'),(313,63,4,'Cancun Underwater Museum','Snorkel at the Cancun Underwater Museum, exploring submerged sculptures that form an artificial reef teeming with marine life. Wander the Interactive Aquarium, touching starfish and watching dolphin shows. Savor a farewell dinner of lobster, toasting to Cancun’s tropical allure.'),(314,64,1,'Playa Delfines & Cancun','Lounge on Playa Delfines, diving into the warm Caribbean for a refreshing swim. Stroll the Hotel Zone’s vibrant boardwalk