INSERT INTO `hotels` VALUES (1,36,1,'Ritz Paris','15 Place Vendôme, 75001 Paris, France','Since its opening in 1898, the Ritz Paris has epitomized luxury and elegance. Following a £112 million renovation, the hotel seamlessly blends historic charm with modern conveniences, offering opulent rooms adorned with canopied beds, silk drapes, and gold-plated fixtures.',2000,176),(2,37,1,'Le Meurice – Dorchester Collection','228 Rue de Rivoli, 1st arr., 75001 Paris, France','Established in 1835, Le Meurice is considered France`s first palace hotel, offering a blend of historical grandeur and contemporary comfort. Overlooking the Tuileries Garden, the hotel features rooms designed in a modern Louis XVI style with views of landmarks from the Louvre to La Défense.',1400,181),(3,38,1,'Four Seasons Hotel George V','31 Avenue George V, 75008 Paris, France','Situated just off the Champs-Élysées, the Four Seasons Hotel George V is renowned for its luxurious accommodations and exceptional service. The hotel features opulent rooms and suites, many with private terraces offering stunning views of Paris. The interiors are adorned with exquisite floral arrangements by Jeff Leatham.',1000,186),(4,39,1,'Hôtel Plaza Athénée – Dorchester Collection','25 Avenue Montaigne, 8th arr., 75008 Paris, France​','Located on the fashionable Avenue Montaigne, Hôtel Plaza Athénée is celebrated for its belle époque architecture and art nouveau façade adorned with red geraniums. The hotel offers rooms with views of the Eiffel Tower and is in close proximity to luxury boutiques.',1796,191),(5,40,2,'Hotel Le Negresco','37 Promenade des Anglais, 06000 Nice, France','An iconic Belle Époque landmark overlooking the Baie des Anges, Le Negresco is a national historic monument renowned for its art-filled interiors and opulent design. Each room is uniquely decorated, blending antique elegance with modern comforts. The hotel houses a Michelin-starred restaurant, Le Chantecler, and offers personalized concierge services.​',500,196),(6,41,2,'Anantara Plaza Nice Hotel','12 Avenue de Verdun, 06000 Nice, France','Housed in a restored 19th-century building, Anantara Plaza offers contemporary luxury with panoramic views of the Mediterranean. Guests can enjoy the rooftop restaurant SEEN by Olivier, a wellness spa, and proximity to the city`s main attractions. The hotel`s design seamlessly blends historic charm with modern amenities.​',450,201),(7,42,2,'Hyatt Regency Nice Palais de la Méditerranée','13 Promenade des Anglais, 06000 Nice, France','This Art Deco gem offers stunning sea views and a blend of classic architecture with contemporary luxury. Guests can relax at the indoor and outdoor pools, dine at the on-site restaurant, and explore nearby cultural sites. The hotel is known for its spacious rooms and exceptional service.​',400,206),(8,43,2,'Hôtel du Couvent','3 Rue de l`Abbaye, 06300 Nice, France​','A former 17th-century convent transformed into a luxury hotel, Hôtel du Couvent offers a unique blend of history and modernity. The property features 88 elegantly appointed rooms, a spa with Turkish baths, and multiple dining options. Its serene gardens and historical architecture provide a tranquil retreat in the heart of Nice.​',600,211),(9,44,3,'Four Seasons Hotel Madrid','Calle de Sevilla, 3, 28014 Madrid, Spain','Housed within a meticulously restored historic building, the Four Seasons Hotel Madrid offers a blend of classic elegance and modern luxury. Guests can enjoy spacious rooms with panoramic city views, a rooftop restaurant, and a state-of-the-art spa. Its central location provides easy access to Madrid`s cultural landmarks and shopping districts.',1200,216),(10,45,3,'Mandarin Oriental Ritz, Madrid','Plaza de la Lealtad, 5, 28014 Madrid, Spain','A symbol of luxury since 1910, the Mandarin Oriental Ritz combines historical grandeur with contemporary amenities. Located near the Prado Museum, it features opulent rooms, a serene spa, and multiple dining options curated by renowned chefs. The hotel`s recent renovation has enhanced its status as a premier destination in Madrid.',1100,221),(11,46,3,'Gran Hotel Inglés','Calle de Echegaray, 8, 28014 Madrid, Spain','As Madrid`s oldest luxury hotel, Gran Hotel Inglés offers a unique blend of 19th-century charm and modern sophistication. Situated in the literary quarter, it provides guests with elegantly designed rooms, a gourmet restaurant, and a tranquil spa. Its rich history and attentive service make it a standout choice for discerning travelers.',600,226),(12,47,3,'Palacio de los Duques Gran Meliá','Cuesta de Santo Domingo, 5, 28013 Madrid, Spain','Inspired by the works of Velázquez, this former palace offers a regal experience in the heart of Madrid. Guests can enjoy luxurious suites, a rooftop pool with panoramic views, and lush gardens. Its proximity to the Royal Palace and Opera House enhances its appeal to culture enthusiasts.',700,231),(13,48,4,'Mandarin Oriental, Barcelona','Passeig de Gràcia, 38-40, 08007 Barcelona, Spain','Located on the prestigious Passeig de Gràcia, the Mandarin Oriental, Barcelona seamlessly blends contemporary elegance with classic luxury. Guests are treated to spacious rooms and suites, many offering views of the city`s iconic architecture. The hotel boasts a rooftop pool, a world-class spa, and dining options curated by renowned chefs. Its central location provides easy access to Gaudí`s masterpieces and upscale shopping districts.',700,236),(14,49,4,'Hotel Arts Barcelona','Carrer de la Marina, 19-21, 08005 Barcelona, Spain','Towering above the Mediterranean Sea, Hotel Arts Barcelona offers a unique blend of urban sophistication and beachfront relaxation. The hotel`s modern design is complemented by an extensive contemporary art collection. Guests can indulge in the two-Michelin-starred restaurant, unwind at the serene spa, or enjoy the outdoor pools with sea views. Its prime location provides direct access to the beach and vibrant nightlife.',650,241),(15