can enjoy panoramic city views, a serene spa, and gourmet dining, all within a sophisticated atmosphere.',900,286),(24,59,6,'Palazzo Parigi Hotel & Grand Spa','Corso di Porta Nuova, 1, 20121 Milan, Italy','A symbol of grandeur and elegance, Palazzo Parigi Hotel & Grand Spa is situated in the heart of Milan`s fashion district. The hotel boasts opulent interiors, spacious rooms with private terraces, and a magnificent grand spa. Guests can indulge in gourmet dining, relax in the lush garden, or rejuvenate at the expansive wellness center, all while experiencing impeccable service.',950,291),(25,60,7,'Aman Venice','Palazzo Papadopoli, Calle Tiepolo 1364, 30125 Venice, Italy','Housed in the 16th-century Palazzo Papadopoli on the Grand Canal, Aman Venice exudes timeless elegance. With just 24 suites, it offers an intimate atmosphere adorned with frescoed ceilings, gilded mirrors, and historical artifacts. Guests can enjoy serene gardens—rare in Venice—and impeccable service that caters to every need.',1200,296),(26,61,7,'Belmond Hotel Cipriani','Giudecca 10, 30133 Venice, Italy','Situated on Giudecca Island, Belmond Hotel Cipriani offers panoramic views of the Venetian Lagoon and Doge`s Palace. The hotel is renowned for its lush gardens, Olympic-sized swimming pool, and exceptional dining options. Guests can reach St. Mark`s Square via the hotel`s private shuttle boat, combining seclusion with convenience.​',1100,301),(27,62,7,'The Gritti Palace, a Luxury Collection Hotel','Campo Santa Maria del Giglio, 2467, 30124 Venice, Italy','Overlooking the Grand Canal, The Gritti Palace is a restored 15th-century noble residence that epitomizes Venetian opulence. Its rooms feature antique furnishings, Murano glass, and rich fabrics. Guests can indulge in gourmet dining at Club del Doge and participate in cooking classes at the Gritti Epicurean School.',950,306),(28,63,7,'Ca’ Sagredo Hotel','Campo Santa Sofia 4198/99, 30121 Venice, Italy','Housed in a 15th-century pink palazzo designated as a National Monument, Ca’ Sagredo Hotel offers a unique blend of history and luxury. Situated along the Grand Canal, the hotel features original frescoes, grand staircases, and antique furnishings that rival many museums. Its 42 rooms are adorned in traditional Venetian style, providing guests with an authentic and opulent experience.​',900,311),(29,64,8,'The Ritz London','150 Piccadilly, St. James`s, London W1J 9BR, United Kingdom','An iconic symbol of British elegance, The Ritz London has been setting the standard for luxury since 1906. Situated in the heart of Mayfair, it offers guests opulent rooms adorned with Louis XVI-style interiors and world-class service. The hotel`s Michelin-starred restaurant and renowned afternoon tea experience are quintessentially British.',1200,316),(30,65,8,'Claridge`s','Brook Street, Mayfair, London W1K 4HR, United Kingdom','A cornerstone of Mayfair`s luxury scene, Claridge`s combines timeless elegance with contemporary flair. Known for its art deco interiors and impeccable service, the hotel has hosted royalty, celebrities, and discerning travelers alike. Guests can indulge in gourmet dining and unwind in the newly opened spa.',1300,321),(31,66,8,'The Savoy','Strand, London WC2R 0EZ, United Kingdom','Overlooking the River Thames, The Savoy is a blend of Edwardian and Art Deco design, offering guests a unique and luxurious experience. With a history of hosting illustrious figures, the hotel boasts exceptional dining options and a renowned American Bar. Its central location provides easy access to London`s cultural landmarks.​',950,326),(32,67,8,'The Connaught','Carlos Place, Mayfair, London W1K 2AL, United Kingdom','Nestled in the heart of Mayfair, The Connaught is a blend of classic English charm and contemporary sophistication. The hotel features elegantly appointed rooms, a Michelin-starred restaurant, and the world-famous Connaught Bar. Its commitment to personalized service ensures a memorable stay for every guest.',1